Universitario Takes Peru Title
LIMA , December 24 ( Xinhua ) -- Universitario took the tile of the Peruvian championship for the 22nd time after beating Sporting Cristal on penalties following the two-leg final ended 3 - 3 on aggregate Wednesday .
The championship was divided into two stages .
Universitario won the first and Sporting the second .
